2026-05-12T17:34:06.9537485Z 21    <!--
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9537867Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9538045Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9538404Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9538766Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9539115Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9539445Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9539793Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9540488Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9540822Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9541100Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-12T17:34:06.9541251Z 32    -->
